originalText.text: Bilel is an exceptional Real Estate Agent with a wealth of experience in navigating the NYC real estate landscape for buyers and sellers. As an attorney, I get to work with many real estate agents.  I have had the pleasure of working with Bilel on many real estate transactions in NYC (condos and coops), and each of them has been a great success for our mutual clients. Bilel is a true professional, who cares about his clients, and who goes above and beyond to make sure each transaction goes smoothly from beginning to end. I would recommend Bilel to anyone looking to purchase or sell Real Estate in NYC.
